  Removed amarok-2.0.2-r1 as it was added to the tree.

  12 Apr 2009; Jorge Manuel B. S. Vicetto <jmbsvicetto@gentoo.org>
  -media-sound/amarok/amarok-2.0.2.ebuild,
  +media-sound/amarok/amarok-2.0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Bumped amarok-2.0.2 ebuild to avoid issues related to the changes in the
  dep introduced without a bump that will make +kdeprefix users lose their
  mind trying to diagnose.

  31 Mar 2009; Maciej Mrozowski (reavertm) <reavertm@poczta.fm>
  amarok-2.0.2.ebuild:
  Dropped kdeprefix, fixed deps (webkit removed - in kdelibs, removed
  duplicated OPENGL_REQUIRED, fixed phonon deps)

  29 Mar 2009; Jorge Manuel B. S. Vicetto <jmbsvicetto@gentoo.org>
  -media-sound/amarok/files/2.0.2-ipod.patch,
  +media-sound/amarok/files/amarok-ipod.patch:
  Updating amarok-2.0.2 to get it to build with qt4.5.

  25 Mar 2009; Theo Chatzimichos <tampakrap@gentoo.org>
  files/2.0.2-ipod.patch, +files/disable_bindings_test.patch,
  amarok-9999.ebuild:
