  stucks on +kdeprefix,

  22 Mar 2009; Maciej Mrozowski (reavertm) <reavertm@poczta.fm>
  amarok-9999.ebuild:
  Added qtscriptgenerator deps

  19 Mar 2009; Maciej Mrozowski (reavertm) <reavertm@poczta.fm>
