  Amarok now requires taglib-extras

  19 Mar 2009; Maciej Mrozowski (reavertm) <reavertm@poczta.fm>
  -files/2.0.2-qt4.5-script.patch, amarok-2.0.2.ebuild, amarok-9999.ebuild:
